Description:

Continuation of the Lights Out kata (Kata4).

We have a 4x4 grid of elements
Each element has two possible states (on/off)
When you step on an element, the adjacent tiles (up, down, left, right) change state, but NOT the tile you're standing on
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
New in this version:
- The grid state persists between moves
- The game ends when all tiles are in the same state (all on or all off)
- The initial grid layout is customizable
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
To try this program, just run: "php YourFileDirectory/LightsOut2.php" on the terminal and voilà! To quit the program, just press ctrl + c on the terminal.
